{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hackers-js","path":"/hackers/collaboration.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>You can collaborate with other hackers in finding vulnerabilities for the programs you’re a part of. This enables you and other collaborating hackers to share resources and any knowledge you each may have about a vulnerability as you work together to uncover security issues. Collaboration is a great way to find vulnerabilities as putting multiple heads together may be better than just one.</p>\n<p>If you’re collaborating with other hackers, you can <a href=\"https://docs.hackerone.com/hackers/payments.html#bounty-splitting\">split the bounty amount</a> so that each hacker is rewarded appropriately. In addition, each collaborator on the report will earn reputation points for their contribution. </p>\n<p>To let other hackers know that you’re open to collaboration:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to your profile’s <strong>Settings > Collaboration Settings</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click the toggle to be <strong>ON</strong> for each of the programs you’re open to collaborating on. The list of programs that appear will include all private programs you’re a part of as well as all public programs you’ve submitted a report to.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"collaboration preferences\"\n        title=\"collaboration preferences\"\n        src=\"/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/0b533/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/fac75/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 125w,\n/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/63868/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 250w,\n/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/0b533/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 500w,\n/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/1d69c/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 750w,\n/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/00d43/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 1000w,\n/static/ec1f4ac2fb2de11ab24db5e506dec244/29007/collaboration_preferences_apr_2021.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Once you’ve selected the programs you’re open to collaborating on, the security page of the program will have a <strong>Collaborators</strong> tab where you can view all of the other hackers that are open to collaborating and be able to contact them so that you can work together.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"collaborators security page\"\n        title=\"collaborators security page\"\n        src=\"/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/0b533/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/fac75/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 125w,\n/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/63868/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 250w,\n/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/0b533/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 500w,\n/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/1d69c/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 750w,\n/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/00d43/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 1000w,\n/static/ee8484d8843f8447b88af0caf9dce4a9/29007/collaborators_security_page_tab_apr_2021.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Collaboration","id":"hackers/collaboration","path":"/hackers/collaboration.html","description":null},"headings":[]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}